179
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,560
Why do you

180
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:07,480
keep talking?

181
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:09,760
I don't think I will

182
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:11,800
