199
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,800
They were nothing!

200
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:56,240
They deserved to die!

201
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,920
Even as ghosts,

202
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:59,240
